
How to use SeleniumGrid
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P5CLXIC7x5c

1. https://www.selenium.dev/documentation/grid/getting_started/
2. Download drivers, put them into path. Or you can put them in the same location of selenium server
3. Run hub
java -jar selenium-server-4.4.0.jar hub
4. Run node on local machine
java -jar selenium-server-4.4.0.jar node --detect-drivers true
5. Virtual machine
5.1. Download drivers, put them into path. Or you can put them in the same location of selenium server
5.2. Run node on wirtual machine
java -jar selenium-server-4.4.0.jar node --detect-drivers true --publish-events tcp://192.168.1.11:4442 --subscribe-events tcp://192.168.1.11:4443